import React, { useState } from 'react'; import '../styles/Properties.css'; const Properties = () => { const [filters, setFilters] = useState({ priceRange: '', propertyType: '', bedrooms: '', location: '' }); const properties = [ { id: 1, title: "Modern Luxury Villa", price: 1250000, location: "Beverly Hills, CA", type: "Villa", bedrooms: 5, bathrooms: 4, area: "4,500 sqft", image: "/images/luxury-villa.jpg", description: "Stunning modern villa with panoramic views", features: ["Swimming Pool", "Garden", "Smart Home", "Security System"] }, { id: 2, title: "Downtown Penthouse", price: 850000, location: "Manhattan, NY", type: "Penthouse", bedrooms: 3, bathrooms: 2, area: "2,200 sqft", image: "/images/penthouse.jpg", description: "Luxurious penthouse with city skyline views", features: ["Terrace", "Gym", "Parking", "Concierge"] }, { id: 3, title: "Seaside Beach House", price: 975000, location: "Malibu, CA", type: "House", bedrooms: 4, bathrooms: 3, area: "3,200 sqft", image: "/images/property1.jpg", description: "Beautiful beachfront property with private access", features: ["Beach Access", "Deck", "Ocean View", "Garage"] }, { id: 4, title: "Urban Loft Apartment", price: 550000, location: "Chicago, IL", type: "Apartment", bedrooms: 2, bathrooms: 2, area: "1,800 sqft", image: "/images/property2.jpg", description: "Contemporary loft in prime downtown location", features: ["High Ceilings", "Open Plan", "Modern Kitchen", "Storage"] }, { id: 5, title: "Mountain View Cabin", price: 425000, location: "Aspen, CO", type: "Cabin", bedrooms: 3, bathrooms: 2, area: "2,000 sqft", image: "/images/rental1.jpg", description: "Cozy cabin with breathtaking mountain views", features: ["Fireplace", "Deck", "Mountain View", "Furnished"] }, { id: 6, title: "Suburban Family Home", price: 720000, location: "Austin, TX", type: "House", bedrooms: 4, bathrooms: 3, area: "3,000 sqft", image: "/images/rental2.jpg", description: "Spacious family home in quiet neighborhood", features: ["Garden", "Garage", "Basement", "Patio"] } ]; const handleFilterChange = (e) => { const { name, value } = e.target; setFilters(prev => ({ ...prev, [name]: value })); }; const filteredProperties = properties.filter(property => { return ( (!filters.priceRange || property.price <= parseInt(filters.priceRange)) && (!filters.propertyType || property.type === filters.propertyType) && (!filters.bedrooms || property.bedrooms >= parseInt(filters.bedrooms)) && (!filters.location || property.location.toLowerCase().includes(filters.location.toLowerCase())) ); }); return (

Find Your Perfect Property

{filteredProperties.map(property => (
${property.price.toLocaleString()}
{property.type}

{property.title}

{property.location}

{property.description}

{property.bedrooms} Beds {property.bathrooms} Baths {property.area}
{property.features.map((feature, index) => ( {feature} ))}
))}
); }; export default Properties;
